+# Publishing a blog — source map
+
+Every claim in `SKILL.md` traces to a line below. Re-derive against the current
+tree before trusting any line number; the behavior is the contract, the line is
+a pointer. The CLI lives in the multica repo (`server/...`); the API it calls
+lives in a separate repo under `inair-addons/inair_website_blog/` — both are
+listed.
+
+## The CLI commands and flags (`multica blog`)
+
+| Fact | Source |
+| --- | --- |
+| `blogCmd` parent + `blog`/`publish`/`list`/`get`/`update` subcommands | `server/cmd/multica/cmd_blog.go:48,63,70,81,88` |
+| Registered on the root: `rootCmd.AddCommand(blogCmd)` | `server/cmd/multica/main.go:90` |
+| `publish` flags: `--title` (required), `--file`, `--blog`, `--subtitle`, `--tag` (repeatable), `--publish`, `--output` | `server/cmd/multica/cmd_blog.go:104-110` |
+| `update` flags: `--title`, `--subtitle`, `--file`, `--tag` (repeatable), `--publish`, `--output` | `server/cmd/multica/cmd_blog.go:114-118` |
+| `--publish=false` unpublishes (bool flag, `Changed`-gated) | `server/cmd/multica/cmd_blog.go:118,309-311` |
+| `--file` reads a file; otherwise stdin is read for content | `server/cmd/multica/cmd_blog.go:196-209` |
+| `--title` required on publish (empty → error) | `server/cmd/multica/cmd_blog.go:189-192` |
+| `--blog` parsed as int64, sent as `blog_id`; default 0 = use agent blog | `server/cmd/multica/cmd_blog.go:106,217-220` |
+
+## The draft-by-default + Markdown contract (CLI side)
+
+| Fact | Source |
+| --- | --- |
+| `publish` sends `is_published: false` unless `--publish` | `server/cmd/multica/cmd_blog.go:214-215,227-228` |
+| `publish` sends `content_format: "markdown"` | `server/cmd/multica/cmd_blog.go:214` |
+| `update` sends `content_format: "markdown"` only when `--file` is set | `server/cmd/multica/cmd_blog.go:296-303` |
+| Tags sent as `tag_names` (string array); update replaces | `server/cmd/multica/cmd_blog.go:224-225,305-307` |
+| `list` → `GET /inair_website_blog/blogs` | `server/cmd/multica/cmd_blog.go:173` |
+| `publish` → `POST /inair_website_blog/posts` | `server/cmd/multica/cmd_blog.go:239` |
+| `get` → `GET /inair_website_blog/posts/<id>` | `server/cmd/multica/cmd_blog.go:270` |
+| `update` → `PATCH /inair_website_blog/posts/<id>` | `server/cmd/multica/cmd_blog.go:314` |
+| Response decoded into `blogPostDTO{ID,Name,Subtitle,BlogID,BlogName,IsPublished,TagNames,URL}` | `server/cmd/multica/cmd_blog.go:35-45` |
+| Human output prints `Post <id> drafted/published in "<blog>".` then `URL: <url>` | `server/cmd/multica/cmd_blog.go:249-256` |
+
+## Zero-config auth (Odoo backend mode)
+
+| Fact | Source |
+| --- | --- |
+| `MULTICA_BACKEND_MODE=odoo` sets `PathPrefix="/multica/agent"`, `OdooBackend=true`, `APIKey` from `MULTICA_ODOO_API_KEY` | `server/internal/cli/client.go:168-173` |
+| `setHeaders` sends `X-GALAXY-ACCESS-TOKEN: Bearer <token>` and `X-GALAXY-API-KEY` only in Odoo mode | `server/internal/cli/client.go:187-203` |
+| `url()` rewrites only paths starting with `/api`; `/inair_website_blog/...` is passed through untouched | `server/internal/cli/client.go:177-185` |
+| `newAPIClient` bypasses the `mat_` task-token requirement in Odoo mode | `server/cmd/multica/cmd_agent.go:262-266` |
+| CLI >=400 responses funnel to `*HTTPError` so exit codes classify 401/403/404 | `server/internal/cli/client.go:67-91` |
+
+## The API contract (inair_website_blog, cross-repo)
+
+Paths are relative to the `inair_website_blog` Odoo module (repo
+`inair-addons/inair_website_blog`, branch `inair-1.0.19-dev`, commit `aa3c316`).
+
+| Fact | Source |
+| --- | --- |
+| All four routes use `auth='openapi'`, `type='http'`, `csrf=False` | `inair_website_blog/controllers/blog_api.py` (route decorators) |
+| `POST /inair_website_blog/posts` validates `name`, resolves blog, creates `blog.post`, returns `201 {id,name,blog_id,blog_name,is_published,url}` | `inair_website_blog/controllers/blog_api.py` (`create_post`) |
+| `is_published` defaults to `bool(data.get('is_published'))` → draft | `inair_website_blog/controllers/blog_api.py` (`create_post`) |
+| Markdown content converted via `from inair_multica.utils import md_to_html` | `inair_website_blog/controllers/blog_api.py` (`_convert_content`) |
+| Blog resolution order: `blog_id` → config `inair_website_blog.default_blog_id` → seeded `inair_website_blog.blog_agent` → first blog | `inair_website_blog/controllers/blog_api.py` (`_resolve_blog`) |
+| `AccessError` → `403 {error}`; missing title → `400`; no blog → `400` | `inair_website_blog/controllers/blog_api.py` (`_catch_access_error`, handlers) |
+
+## The agent-dedicated blog + permission group (inair_website_blog)
+
+| Fact | Source |
+| --- | --- |
+| Seeded blog `inair_website_blog.blog_agent` named 「智能体技术文档」 (draft area), `noupdate=1` | `inair_website_blog/data/inair_blog_data.xml` |
+| Default-blog setting `inair_blog_default_blog_id` (`res.config.settings`, config_parameter) | `inair_website_blog/models/res_config_settings.py` |
+| Group `group_inair_blog_author` implies `website.group_website_designer` (which holds blog.post/blog.blog/blog.tag write ACLs) | `inair_website_blog/security/inair_website_blog_security.xml` |
+| website_blog's write/create ACLs are gated on `website.group_website_designer` | `odoo/addons/website_blog/security/ir.model.access.csv` (upstream) |
